{"tid":158812,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"要 峇里 定要 關島？！","createTime":"2017-03-16T14:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T17:15:37.000Z","uid":24524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25de4b78f57cdf8b10074306613b081147112da3","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"論景色<br />\n論環境、設施<br />\n論飲食<br />\n論消費<br />\n論人文<br />\n論治安<br />\n有冇巴打去過兩度可以簡略講下兩者優劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：兩度都未去過亦都有興趣去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c524b447c2ed1518f8501f378f023be60de461b3","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a08f523a7bcb2384dd11f0f481f91dcd3df0c71","tid":158812,"uid":38376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"去關島同峇里嘅消費好唔同，比得起梗係去關島<br />\n<br />\n關島係屬於美國，峇里係印尼<br />\n<br />\n關島係陽光海灘水上活動為主，然後就有周邊d島睇風景啊古蹟咁，行吓美式mall同outlet，在亞洲感受美國式悠閒，美色早午晚餐。治安感覺上唔錯。可惜早午晚餐比較貴。<br />\n<br />\n峇里都係陽光海灘水上活動，其次就有梯田有出名嘅廟等景點，講relex都唔差，唔同國家crusine都有價錢有平有貴。不過交通方面係好塞車，而且貌似當地都怕有襲擊咁所以部分酒店係要scan車底過安檢咁<br />\n<br />\n我嘅感覺就係，文化/生活黎講關島好似感受嘅野多d咁，但景點的話峇里島會多d款色"},{"pid":"b6c671cbdb57477d0c1cd37510a12af09d56e719","tid":158812,"uid":78669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:24:33.000Z","msg":"只係去過峇里。<br />\n講食，ubud好多西餐廳都好食，價錢又平。酒店早餐都好豐富。而本地人食嘅嘢就麻麻地。<br />\n講景色，有沙灘、懸崖、火山、梯田、廟。<br />\n講玩，可以join local tour踩單車、划艇等等。反而浮潛同潛水就不了。<br />\n交通就要book司機，市中心好塞車。<br />\n峇里人好人到不得了，治安好好。"},{"pid":"383dc125c32a1cd7b4dead57d65fb9eb27509266","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去關島同峇里嘅消費好唔同，比得起梗係去關島<br />\n<br />\n關島係屬於美國，峇里係印尼<br />\n<br />\n關島係陽光海灘水上活動為主，然後就有周邊d島睇風景啊古蹟咁，行吓美式mall同outlet，在亞洲感受美國式悠閒，美色早午晚餐。治安感覺上唔錯。可惜早午晚餐比較貴。<br />\n<br />\n峇里都係陽光海灘水上活動，其次就有梯田有出名嘅廟等景點，講relex都唔差，唔同國家crusine都有價錢有平有貴。不過交通方面係好塞車，而且貌似當地都怕有襲擊咁所以部分酒店係要scan車底過安檢咁<br />\n<br />\n我嘅感覺就係，文化/生活黎講關島好似感受嘅野多d咁，但景點的話峇里島會多d款色</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cac3446f0e27ebd6610b0d33714d137031ec6b","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只係去過峇里。<br />\n講食，ubud好多西餐廳都好食，價錢又平。酒店早餐都好豐富。而本地人食嘅嘢就麻麻地。<br />\n講景色，有沙灘、懸崖、火山、梯田、廟。<br />\n講玩，可以join local tour踩單車、划艇等等。反而浮潛同潛水就不了。<br />\n交通就要book司機，市中心好塞車。<br />\n峇里人好人到不得了，治安好好。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f3c0286abae6385df24ece536b5fa43e3be8b8","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fd6a206bcc6c1d8048bb60bac3f3638df3aeef","tid":158812,"uid":50568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T15:28:34.000Z","msg":"有同樣煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fc83fb0f1df2921b849528a61df125ac954639","tid":158812,"uid":24524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有同樣煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfaf1c421a1dcc8f7dc6907cbc0dc70990f94b01","tid":158812,"uid":37131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"打算黎緊去峇里<br />\n留個名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無峇里既酒店介紹？"}]}